(5108, 4142, 'main_template_2_text', '<h2>ABOUT US</h2>\r\nThe Enhanced Developmental &amp; Learning Intervention Program (EDLIP) is for preschoolers with mild developmental needs from the ages of 4 to 8 in\r\npreparation for primary education. Unfortunately in Singapore, there are limited kindergartens that offers a holistic curriculum for children with developmental\r\nneeds where the child is prepared sufficiently for the demands of primary education. Even if a kindergarten for developmental needs is found, most have a\r\nhigh student to teacher ratio, which makes it difficult for the child to fully benefit from the program.\r\n\r\nThe Enhanced Developmental &amp; Learning Intervention Program (EDLIP) is for preschoolers with mild developmental needs from the ages of 4 to 8 in\r\npreparation for primary education. Unfortunately in Singapore, there are limited kindergartens that offers a holistic curriculum for children with developmental\r\nneeds where the child is prepared sufficiently for the demands of primary education. Even if a kindergarten for developmental needs is found, most have a\r\nhigh student to teacher ratio, which makes it difficult for the child to fully benefit from the program.'),
