(6539, 4269, 'main_template_0_text', '<strong>Mr Chia Lee Hwe</strong>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"position\">Director of Education &amp; Operations </span>\r\n\r\nMr. Chia co-founded Cognitive Development Learning Centre Pte Ltd in 2009 and is the Director of the company. He holds an MBA in Finance from University of Leeds and a Diploma in Learning Disorder from the College of Allied Educators.\r\n\r\nHe was a Member in the Advisory Committee of a Primary School for 7 years. He also won his recognition from Ministry of Education (MOE) and was awarded for his Services to Education in 2009.'),
