(6554, 4269, '_main_template_2_title', 'field_60ec47058886c'),
(6555, 4269, 'main_template_2_subtitle', 'Cognitive employs a stringent selection process that ensures our teachers are skilled practitioners in their area of expertise with years of experience. Our Teaching Specialists are trained in the field of Education, Psychology and Special Needs Education. They have the passion for teaching and are familiar with the current MOE syllabus.\r\n\r\nOur specialists dedicate time and effort to understand each and every child in our learning centre. We specialise in developing bespoke and unique strategies to overcome their learning difficulties and enhance their academic and behaviourial development.'),
