(7433, 4294, 'main_template_1_text', 'Cognitive Development Learning Centre’s Speech Training Program supports children in terms of language, ﬂuency, social &amp; cognitive skills, voice and literacy skills.\r\n\r\nThis include:\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Understanding reading text</li>\r\n<li>Sustaining conversation and/or discussion</li>\r\n<li>Voice and tempo control</li>\r\n<li>Social etiquette during conversation</li>\r\n<li>Expressing thoughts and feelings in a conﬁdent manner</li>\r\n<li>Pronounce words accurately and clearly</li>\r\n<li>Enhancing mouth and jaw ﬂexibility through exercises</li>\r\n<li>Reading and writing skills</li>\r\n<li>Attention and conﬁdence building activities</li>\r\n	<li>Fluency in conversation</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n'),
